headline.main: Elgar and Wagner Keen to Renew Schoolboy Rivalry
headline.print_headline: Elgar and Wagner Keen to Renew Schoolboy Rivalry

lead_paragraph: Dean Elgar and Neil Wagner hope to renew a rivalry that began in feisty schoolboy matches in the Highveld when South Africa face New Zealand in the first test in Dunedin this week.
